(1, 'Contact Us', 'contact_us', 'Contact Us', 1, 0, 0, 1, '2010-04-29 08:55:42', '<p>Details for all Arena Group sites are below . If you wish to contact our board or leave us feedback, you can do so by filling in <a href="../../../page/let-the-board-know">this form</a>.</p>\r\n<p><em>Calls are monitored for quality and training purposes.</em></p>\r\n<p><a name="Wakefield"></a></p>\r\n<h2>Service and supplies for print and copy</h2>\r\n<p>Service Telephone: 0344 863 8008<br />Service E-mail: <a href="mailto:service@arenagroup.net">service@arenagroup.net</a><br />Professional Services Email: <a href="mailto:EDMsupport@arenagroup.net">PSsupport@arenagroup.net</a></p>\r\n<h2>Service and queries for scanning devices and electronic document management (mstore):</h2>\r\n<p>EDM Support Telephone: 0344 863 8010<br />EDM Support Email: <a href="mailto:EDMsupport@arenagroup.net">EDMsupport@arenagroup.net</a></p>\r\n<h2>General queries, Sales and HR enquiries:</h2>\r\n<p>Telephone: 0344 863 8000<br />General E-mail: <a href="mailto:info@arenagroup.net">info@arenagroup.net</a> <br />Sales E-mail: <a href="mailto:sales@arenagroup.net">sales@arenagroup.net</a><br />Fax: 0113 288 0671</p>\r\n<h2>Arena Group Ltd, Wakefield</h2>\r\n<p>Armitage House<br />Thorpe Lower Lane<br />Robin Hood<br />Wakefield<br />WF3 3BQ</p>\r\n<p>Directions: <a href="../../../assets/stored_documents/original/115_Wakefield_Map.pdf" target="_blank">Map</a></p>\r\n<p><a name="Atherton"></a></p>\r\n<h2>Arena Group Ltd, Lancashire</h2>\r\n<p>No. 13 The Quad<br />Atherleigh Business Park<br />Atherton<br />Greater Manchester<br />M46 0SY</p>\r\n<p>Directions: <a href="../../../assets/stored_documents/original/77_Bolton_Quad_v2_Map.pdf" target="_blank">Map</a></p>\r\n<p><a name="Chesterfield"></a></p>\r\n<h2>Arena Group Ltd, Chesterfield</h2>\r\n<p>Unit 2, Hillstown Business Centre<br />Mansfield Road<br />Hillstown<br />Chesterfield<br />S44 6LE</p>\r\n<p><a name="NE"></a></p>\r\n<h2>Arena Group Ltd, North East</h2>\r\n<p>Suite 32<br />Durham Tees Valley Business Centre<br />Primrose Hill Industrial Estate<br />Orde Wingate Way<br />Stockton-on-Tees<br />TS19 0GA</p>\r\n<p>Directions: <a href="../../../assets/stored_documents/original/114_NE_Map.pdf" target="_blank">Map</a></p>\r\n<p><a name="EDM"></a></p>\r\n<h2>Distribution and Training Centre</h2>\r\n<p>Arena Group Ltd<br />Unit D<br />Lotherton Business Park<br />Lotherton Way<br />Garforth<br />Leeds<br />LS25 2HP</p>\r\n<p>Directions: <a href="../../../assets/stored_documents/original/17_Garforth_Map.pdf" target="_blank">Map</a></p>\r\n<p><a name="Fovia"></a></p>\r\n<h2>Fovia (Innovation) Ltd</h2>\r\n<p>5 Swinegate<br />Grantham<br />Lincolnshire<br />NG31 6RJ</p>\r\n<p>Directions: <a href="../../../assets/stored_documents/original/113_Grantham_Map.pdf" target="_blank">Map</a></p>', '2010-06-29 15:18:17', '2015-06-19 09:13:48', '', '', NULL, 7, 0, NULL, 1, 0),
(2, 'Products and Services', 'services', 'Our Consultative Approach', 2, 0, 0, 1, '2010-04-29 08:55:42', '<p class="introduction"><img style="float: right;" src="../../../assets/page_contents/2/contained_images/08441be97b3b_228_iStock_000006828102Large.jpg?1376295279" border="0" alt="" hspace="10" vspace="10" width="250" />Research has shown that print spend accounts for 1 - 3% of annual revenue.</p>\r\n<p>Addressing your print and copy strategy in isolation can deliver   cost savings and a more efficient way of working. 				We also know that  organisations spend between 5 and 15% of their  annual revenue on  document lifecycle costs. 				So, a broader approach that considers the  way you work with  documents across the board will deliver a much more  significant  financial cost saving.</p>\r\n<p>With this in mind, our consultancy service addresses the way your organisation works   with both paper and digital documents with the aim of promoting efficiency,  				reducing waste and minimising costs.</p>\r\n<p>Solutions range from relatively simple ideas that focus on just one  element of your document workflow. 				For example, we may look at  digitising a paper archive or your mailroom. 				We could address a  particular paper-driven process such as purchase order processing; 				 or look at refining your print and copy systems and practices.</p>\r\n<p>Alternatively, we may review and improve the way you work with  documents across the board, 				enhancing your technical infrastructure  and integrating new tools and practices to drive efficiency, 				reduce  costs and minimise waste in all areas of document management including  creation, processing, storage and disposal.</p>\r\n<h2>Download our free guides</h2>\r\n<p>Deciding on an appropriate document management strategy can be difficult and a consultation with one of our experts can very quickly point you in the right direction. In the meantime we have produced a number of helpful guides which you can use to help you answer some basic questions.</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><a href="../../../free-guides-31-ways-to-reduce-paper-usage.pdf">31 Ways to Reduce Paper Usage</a></li>\r\n<li><a href="../../../free-guides-managing-mobile-devices-in-the-workplace.pdf">Managing Mobile Devices in the Workplace</a></li>\r\n<li><a href="../../../free-guides-top-tips-for-selecting-a-managed-print-service-provider.pdf">Top Tips for Selecting a Managed Print Service Provider</a></li>\r\n<li><a href="../../../free-guides-top-tips-on-data-protection.pdf">Top Tips on Data Protection</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2>Useful Links</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><a href="../../../articles/110">Questioning the Cost of Purchasing</a></li>\r\n<li><a href="../../../page/print-the-hidden-costs">The Hidden Costs of Print</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', '2010-11-23 12:48:09', '2014-04-25 14:12:56', '', '', 1, 3, 0, NULL, 1, 0),
(3, 'Products', 'product_catalogue', 'Products', 3, 0, 0, 1, '2010-04-29 08:55:42', 'The front page of the products catalogue.', '2010-11-23 12:49:03', '2011-01-12 12:11:42', '', '', 1, 1, 0, NULL, 1, 0),
(4, 'Apprenticeship Academy', 'our_engineers', 'Apprenticeship Academy', 4, 0, 0, 1, '2010-04-29 08:55:42', '<p class="introduction"><img class="image_right" src="../../../assets/page_contents/4/contained_images/d9e0bf63f2c9_17_engineers_john_crookes.jpg?1295345858" border="0" alt="" hspace="0" vspace="0" width="250" />Arena supports apprenticeships for staff in a variety of roles across the business including administration, IT and service.</p>\r\n<p>We are proud to have been awarded the accolade of <a href="../../../articles/195">Employer of The Year from the Leeds Apprenticeship Awards</a> for two years running. This is in recognition of our outstanding committment to apprentices across the business.</p>\r\n<p>Amy Cheung took up an apprenticeship in Business Administration whilst working in Arena''s Administration Team in order to earn formal qualifications alongside work experience. Amy told us; <em><span class="font_blue">&ldquo;After college I wanted to be working and earning whilst I continued to study, instead of being stuck in a classroom. My job at Arena is varied as I am given opportunities to train in different areas of the business, such as finance, which makes the work really interesting.&rdquo;</span></em></p>\r\n<p>We have run our own apprenticeship programme to train our service engineers  since 1994. Our five year apprenticeship combines training in the latest  technologies with customer care skills.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Technical support manager John Crookes joined Arena&rsquo;s Apprenticeship Academy 10 years ago straight from school after his GCSEs. He now supports a team of engineers and is still on the road himself.</p>\r\n<p class="font_blue"><em>&ldquo;I&rsquo;ve grown up at Arena. I joined the apprenticeship programme at 16, not really knowing what I wanted to do. But it was clear that I could progress here and there were good incentives to encourage me. The best bit of my job is going out and meeting our customers. It&rsquo;s important to build a relationship with them.&nbsp; We&rsquo;re not simply fixing a machine, but helping a client.&rdquo;&nbsp;</em></p>\r\n<p>21-year-old Craig Russell joined Arena&rsquo;s apprenticeship programme just over two years&rsquo; ago; <em><span class="font_blue">&ldquo;we get the very best training, including the chance to learn from big manufacturers such as Toshiba and Kyocera.&nbsp; Being able to work on the very latest machines is a real help with my job.&rdquo;</span></em></p>\r\n<h2>Further information</h2>\r\n<p>To find out more about the Apprenticeship Academy or to apply for a place please <a href="../../../web/contact_us">contact us</a>.</p>\r\n<h2>Downloads:</h2>\r\n<p><a href="../../../assets/stored_documents/original/78_Admin apprentice.pdf" target="_blank">Evie: A day in the life of an Arena admin apprentice</a></p>\r\n<p><a href="../../../assets/stored_documents/original/80_Service apprentice.pdf" target="_blank">Tom: A day in the life of an Arena service apprentice</a></p>\r\n<p><a href="../../../assets/stored_documents/original/79_IT apprentice.pdf" target="_blank">Mark: A day in the life of an Arena IT apprentice</a></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', '2010-11-23 12:50:26', '2014-04-24 07:57:28', '', '', 1, 3, 0, NULL, 1, 0),
(6, 'Online Support', 'customer_care', 'Online Support', 6, 0, 0, 1, '2010-04-29 08:55:42', '<p class="introduction">We pride ourselves on our commitment to excellent customer service. All Arena employees sign up to our <strong>Six Golden Rules </strong>for providing outstanding customer service.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>From our backroom team that parcel up the toners for your printers to  our sales team and service engineers, everyone follows the rules:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>&nbsp;&nbsp; Answer your phone</li>\r\n<li>&nbsp;&nbsp; Don&rsquo;t make promises unless you will keep them</li>\r\n<li>&nbsp;&nbsp; Listen to your customers</li>\r\n<li>&nbsp;&nbsp; Deal with complaints</li>\r\n<li>&nbsp;&nbsp; Be helpful</li>\r\n<li>&nbsp;&nbsp; Take the extra step.</li>\r\n</ul>', '2010-11-23 12:52:34', '2013-01-23 15:34:08', '', '', 1, 1, 0, NULL, 1, 0),
(7, 'Testimonials', 'testimonials', 'Testimonials', 7, 0, 0, 1, '2010-04-29 08:55:42', '', '2010-11-23 12:53:20', '2010-11-23 12:53:31', '', '', 1, 1, 0, NULL, 1, 0),
(8, 'Case Studies', 'case_studies', 'Case Studies', 8, 0, 0, 1, '2010-04-29 08:55:42', 'This is the front page of the Case Studies section.', '2010-11-23 12:54:08', '2010-11-26 14:33:13', '', '', 1, 1, 0, NULL, 1, 0),
(9, 'Arena in the Community', 'community', 'Arena in the Community', 9, 0, 0, 1, '2010-04-29 08:55:42', '<p class="introduction"><strong></strong>At Arena we believe in giving back to our community; our CSR scheme contributes the time and skills of our volunteers towards community and charity projects.</p>\r\n<h2>Some of the ways we help:</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Our employees are encouraged to spend  two annual working days supporting local charity and community projects.</li>\r\n<li>Arena is the primary sponsor of the Jane Tomlinson Arena Group Junior Run and Mini Fun Run, paying entry fees for every young competitor. This makes the event the largest free-to-enter race series for young people in Yorkshire.</li>\r\n<li>Our employees have helped with a variety of projects from supporting schools in delivering enterprise projects to hosting charity events and clearing up urban areas.</li>\r\n<li>We match fund our employees&rsquo; charity fundraising efforts.</li>\r\n</ul>', '2010-11-23 12:54:41', '2015-03-03 15:36:34', '', '', 1, 7, 0, NULL, 1, 0),
(10, 'Green Arena', 'green_area', 'Green Arena', 10, 0, 0, 1, '2010-04-29 08:55:42', '<p class="introduction">Arena has its own environmental policy and we know that sustainability is an issue for most of the businesses, organisations, schools, colleges and universities we work with.</p>\r\n<p>We help our customers in a number of ways to be eco-friendly and to achieve sustainability and low carbon targets.</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Energy efficient printers and copiers that use less power and have sleep modes</li>\r\n<li>Bespoke software to minimise unnecessary printing</li>\r\n<li>Machines that print on both sides of the paper</li>\r\n<li>Electronic document management system using our own <strong>m</strong>store software, enables scanning, organisation and retrieval of critical documents and thereby reduces your printing and document storage costs</li>\r\n<li>Recycling of your old printers and related supplies. (Find out about toner cartridge recycling on our <a href="../../../faqs">FAQs</a> page)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2>Supporting Your Environmental Aims</h2>\r\n<p>&ldquo;Leeds Trinity has a carbon management plan that aims to reduce CO2 emissions over five years. It is really important to us that we buy products and services that are energy efficient in line with our goals to be a sustainable campus.&rdquo; - <strong>Leeds Trinity University College.</strong></p>\r\n<p>&ldquo;Reed Boardall has been committed to a &lsquo;green strategy&rsquo; from the early 1990s and the new Electronic Document Management (EDM) system is targeted to reduce paper costs by at least 30%.&rdquo; - <strong>Reed Boardall</strong>,&nbsp;one of the UK&rsquo;s largest temperature controlled food distributors.</p>\r\n<h2>Partners in Sustainability</h2>\r\n<p>Arena Group recognises the importance of working collaboratively with partners to encourage and support common environmental aims. Click the links below to find more information about the environmental aims and activities of our partners:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><a href="http://www.toshiba.eu/eu/Environmental-Management/" target="_blank">Toshiba</a></li>\r\n<li><a href="http://global.kyocera.com/ecology/eco/index.html" target="_blank">Kyocera</a></li>\r\n<li><a href="http://www.ricoh-europe.com/environment/index.xhtml" target="_blank">RICOH</a></li>\r\n<li><a href="http://www.riso.co.uk/240-eco-friendly-printer.htm" target="_blank">RISO</a></li>\r\n<li><a href="http://www.utax.com/C12571420062FB0F/direct/environment" target="_blank">UTAX</a>.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2>Toshiba''s Carbon Zero Scheme</h2>\r\n<p>The environmental scheme from Toshiba ensures that every Toshiba&nbsp;MFP&nbsp;is both helping the environment and making a positive contribution. The first scheme of its kind to be widely offered to MFP customers in the UK, carbon offsetting allows for the investment in projects that save the emission of, or absorb an equivalent amount of co2 to that of the manufacture and&nbsp;shipment of&nbsp;your MFP device.&nbsp;Find out more about the scheme at <a href="http://www.toshibacarbonzero.co.uk" target="_blank">www.toshibacarbonzero.co.uk</a></p>\r\n<p><img src="../../../images/CarbonZeroScheme.gif" border="0" alt="" hspace="0" width="370" /></p>', '2010-11-23 12:55:14', '2015-02-13 11:28:42', '', '', 1, 3, 0, NULL, 1, 0),
(12, 'Customer Resources', 'free_resources', 'Customer Resources', 12, 0, 0, 1, '2010-04-29 08:55:42', '<p><span class="introduction">Resources for customers and survey stats are below.</span></p>', '2010-11-23 12:56:38', '2013-01-23 12:44:06', '', '', 1, 3, 0, NULL, 1, 0),
(13, 'Driver Downloads', 'driver_download', 'Driver Downloads', 13, 0, 0, 1, '2010-04-29 08:55:42', '<p>This page contains links to documentation on our products: brochures, software drivers, product data sheets and more.</p>\r\n<p>These documents can be downloaded and viewed in PDF format using the free <a href="http://get.adobe.com/reader" target="_blank">Adobe Acrobat Reader</a>.</p>\r\n<p>Please note that we cannot be held responsible for the content or the misuse of any file downloaded from any of these locations.</p>\r\n<div class="driver_downloads">\r\n<hr />\r\n<h2>Printer Drivers</h2>\r\n<p><a href="http://www.eid.toshiba.com.au/n_driver_search4.asp" target="_blank"><img src="http://www.arenagroupservice.net/images/toshiba.gif" border="0" alt="" width="100" /></a></p>\r\n<p><a href="http://www.oki.co.uk/fcgi-bin/public.fcgi?cid=125&amp;grid=&amp;pid=6&amp;chid=1" target="_blank"><img src="http://www.arenagroupservice.net/images/oki.gif" border="0" alt="" width="100" /></a></p>\r\n<p><a href="http://www.ricoh-support.com/enduser/downloads/" target="_blank"><img src="http://www.arenagroupservice.net/images/ricoh.gif" border="0" alt="" width="100" /></a></p>\r\n<p><a href="http://www.brother-support.co.uk/" target="_blank"><img src="http://www.arenagroupservice.net/images/brother.gif" border="0" alt="" width="100" /></a></p>\r\n<p><a href="http://support.lexmark.com/index?page=home&amp;locale=EN&amp;userlocale=EN_UK&amp;segment=DOWNLOAD" target="_blank"><img src="http://www.arenagroupservice.net/images/lexmark.gif" border="0" alt="" width="100" /></a></p>\r\n<p><a href="http://www.kyoceramita.co.uk/index/products/download_centre.html" target="_blank"><img src="http://www.arenagroupservice.net/images/kyocera.gif" border="0" alt="" width="100" /></a></p>\r\n<hr />\r\n<h2 class="clear">User Manuals</h2>\r\n<p><a href="http://imaging.toshiba.co.uk/cgi-bin/WebObjects/TPublicPortalUK.woa/wa/toKeyPage?key=dl_uk" target="_blank"><img src="http://www.arenagroupservice.net/images/toshiba.gif" border="0" alt="" width="100" /></a></p>\r\n<p><a href="http://www.oki.co.uk/fcgi-bin/public.fcgi?pid=60&amp;cid=125&amp;chid=1" target="_blank"><img src="http://www.arenagroupservice.net/images/oki.gif" border="0" alt="" width="100" /></a></p>\r\n<p><a href="javascript: alert(''Unfortunately Ricoh only offer replacement manuals through Dealers, please contact us for assistance'')"> <img src="http://www.arenagroupservice.net/images/ricoh.gif" border="0" alt="" width="100" /></a></p>\r\n<p><a href="http://www.brother-support.co.uk/" target="_blank"><img src="http://www.arenagroupservice.net/images/brother.gif" border="0" alt="" width="100" /></a></p>\r\n<p><a href="http://images.lexmark.com/publications/pdfs/2007/index/en.html" target="_blank"><img src="http://www.arenagroupservice.net/images/lexmark.gif" border="0" alt="" width="100" /></a></p>\r\n<p><a href="http://www.kyoceramita.co.uk/index/products/download_centre.html" target="_blank"><img src="http://www.arenagroupservice.net/images/kyocera.gif" border="0" alt="" width="100" /></a></p>\r\n<hr />\r\n</div>', '2010-11-23 12:57:30', '2013-12-16 11:04:58', '', '', 1, 7, 0, NULL, 1, 0),
