(27, 'Let The Board Know', 'care_1', 'Let The Board Know', 27, 0, 0, 1, '2010-04-29 08:55:42', '<p>We welcome feedback from our customers as it can help us to plan and improve our services. Customer satisfaction is core to our overall mission and because of this we regulary survey our customers to find out what they think of us. If you have something to tell us, good or bad, please complete the form below.</p>', '2010-11-23 15:40:57', '2011-02-08 16:05:46', '', '', 1, 1, 0, NULL, 1, 0),
(29, 'Join Our Team', 'hiring', 'Join The Arena Team', 29, 0, 0, 1, '2010-04-29 08:55:42', '<p>Our current business plan requires us to recruit a significant number of high quality individuals over the next three years.</p>\r\n<p>Our philosophy is that motivated employees contribute to customer  retention by providing world class customer service. We therefore invest  in great people, most of whom stay with us for many years.</p>\r\n<h2><a href="../../../page/careers#spot">Click to view current vacancies</a></h2>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><img style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="../../../assets/page_contents/67/contained_images/6600fce5b199_193_170D4638.jpg?1362069055" border="0" alt="" hspace="0" vspace="0" width="250" /></p>\r\n<table style="padding: 0px; text-align: center;" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" width="432" height="0">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style="padding: 0px; text-align: center;" valign="top"><img style="float: left;" src="../../../assets/page_contents/67/contained_images/d86f2d8f991b_190_Red nose day 2011 005.jpg?1361893392" border="0" alt="" hspace="0" vspace="0" width="285" height="188" /></td>\r\n<td style="padding: 0;" valign="top"><img style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="../../../assets/page_contents/67/contained_images/d82e3f2ffa32_192_13.jpg?1361981379" border="0" alt="" hspace="0" vspace="0" width="250" />\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p>We are recognised for our commitment to customers and employees and this is evidenced by a number of awards we have received:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Yorkshire''s Best Company To Work For</li>\r\n<li>Sunday Times 100 Best Small Companies To Work For</li>\r\n<li>National Award For Customer Service Excellence</li>\r\n<li>National Award For People Development</li>\r\n<li>Investors in People</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>We are proud to have been awarded the <a href="../../../articles/165">Investors in People Bronze Accreditation</a>. Having held the standard accreditation since 1997, this shows Arena''s dedication to developing employees.</p>\r\n<p>If you feel you have what it takes to complement our existing team, please contact us &ndash; we&rsquo;d love to hear from you.</p>\r\n<p><a name="spot"></a></p>', '2010-11-23 15:44:00', '2014-12-19 11:56:38', '', '', 1, 7, 0, NULL, 1, 0),
(30, 'Copy and Print', 'copy_and_print', 'Copy and Print', 30, 0, 0, 1, '2010-04-29 08:55:42', '<p class="introduction"><img style="float: right;" src="../../../assets/page_contents/30/contained_images/1c32004de86c_272_iStock_000013268728_WL.jpg?1412951221" border="0" alt="" hspace="10" vspace="10" width="250" />We know there is no &lsquo;one size fits all&rsquo; when it comes to your print and copy strategy.</p>\r\n<p>Yes, we deal in printers and photocopiers but we are so much more than that.</p>\r\n<p>Whether you need one efficient printer or MFD (multi-function   device) or a bespoke <a href="../../../page/print-the-hidden-costs">Managed Print Service (MPS)</a>, we will work with you   to design the best solution for your needs, taking into consideration:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>any special print requirements</li>\r\n<li>how much print and copy you need to produce</li>\r\n<li>necessary controls, reports and/or restrictions</li>\r\n<li>environmental targets</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2 class="no-top">Free savings print review</h2>\r\n<p class="font_blue"><em>Our Managed Print Service could reduce your print and copy costs by up to 30%.</em></p>\r\n<p>Our friendly team conduct a free savings print review looking at your current print and copy devices, volumes, costs and requirements. We then present you with a bespoke review document that explains how we can deliver efficiencies and a better controlled strategy.</p>\r\n<p>Find out more about our <a href="../../../page/print-the-hidden-costs">Managed Print Service</a> (MPS).</p>\r\n<h2>We are Independent</h2>\r\n<p>Because we are an independent supplier we regularly review the market to source the most suitable products for our clients. We work hard to provide a solution that is the right fit for your organisation.</p>\r\n<h2>Download our free guides</h2>\r\n<p>Deciding on an appropriate print and copy strategy can be difficult and a consultation with one of our experts can very quickly point you in the right direction. In the meantime we have produced a number of helpful guides which you can use to help you answer some basic questions.</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><a href="../../../free-guides-31-ways-to-reduce-paper-usage.pdf">31 Ways to Reduce Paper Usage</a></li>\r\n<li><a href="../../../free-guides-managing-mobile-devices-in-the-workplace.pdf">Managing Mobile Devices in the Workplace</a></li>\r\n<li><a href="../../../free-guides-top-tips-for-selecting-a-managed-print-service-provider.pdf">Top Tips for Selecting a Managed Print Service Provider</a></li>\r\n<li><a href="../../../free-guides-top-tips-on-data-protection.pdf">Top Tips on Data Protection</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2>Useful Links</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><a href="../../../articles/110">Questioning the Cost of Purchasing</a></li>\r\n<li><a href="../../../page/print-the-hidden-costs">The hidden costs of print</a></li>\r\n<li><a href="../../../articles/130">The process behind Arena''s tailored Managed Print Service</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n</ul>', '2010-11-25 15:52:21', '2015-05-26 09:31:26', '', '', 1, 7, 0, NULL, 1, 0),
(32, 'Our Managed Print Service (MPS)', 'print_–_the_hidden_costs', 'Our Managed Print Service (MPS)', 37, 0, 0, 1, '2010-04-29 08:55:42', '<p><span class="introduction">Research carried out by Arena shows that print is an unrecognised and often uncontrolled cost in many organisations. Do you know much you spend on print and copy?</span></p>\r\n<h2>Regular findings from&nbsp;our free print audits:</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Over <strong class="font_blue">90%</strong> of organisations have no idea how much they spend on print </li>\r\n<li>A business with over <strong class="font_blue">25 </strong>different&nbsp;brands among their <strong class="font_blue">93 </strong>printers</li>\r\n<li>A housing association was dealing with <strong class="font_blue">10 </strong>different suppliers for printers and consumables </li>\r\n<li>A school had stockpiled toners worth almost <strong class="font_blue">&pound;7,000</strong> &lsquo;in case they ran out&rsquo;</li>\r\n<li>An independent school thought they had <strong class="font_blue">39</strong> printers.&nbsp; In fact they had <strong class="font_blue">89</strong> printers</li>\r\n<li>Many organisations store&nbsp;toner for&nbsp;<strong><span class="font_blue">obsolete printers</span></strong>.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2>What is our Managed Print Service (MPS)?</h2>\r\n<p><a href="../../../articles/130" target="_blank">Check out our infographic: MPS in pictures!&nbsp; </a></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>The right mix of printers and copiers to meet&nbsp; your demands and minimise costs - MPS could reduce your print and copy costs by&nbsp;up to 30%.</li>\r\n<li>Software automatically monitors toners, despatched as you&nbsp;need them</li>\r\n<li>Remote monitoring of your device status</li>\r\n<li>Print, copy and&nbsp;imaging consolidated into one monthly cost</li>\r\n<li>Single monthly&nbsp;invoice &ndash; no surprise bills</li>\r\n<li>Arena can take away old printers and recycle them.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2>Further Information</h2>\r\n<p><a href="../../../case_studies?service=Copy+and+Print">Case studies: MPS customer stories</a></p>\r\n<p><a href="../../../assets/stored_documents/original/98_24_final MPS brochure for email.pdf" target="_blank">MPS Brochure</a></p>\r\n<p><a href="../../../articles/130" target="_blank">Check out our infographic: MPS in pictures!&nbsp; </a></p>\r\n<p><a href="../../../articles/81?tag=Expert+News">5 Top tips towards choosing a managed print provider</a></p>\r\n<p><a href="../../assets/stored_documents/original/7_MPS from Arena Group.pdf" target="_blank">MPS from Arena Group - Case study</a></p>', '2010-11-26 11:43:24', '2015-07-24 13:20:51', '', '', 1, 7, 0, NULL, 1, 0),
(33, 'Electronic Document Management', 'electronic_document_management_edm', 'Electronic Document Management', 38, 0, 0, 1, '2010-04-29 08:55:42', '<p class="introduction"><img style="float: right;" src="../../../assets/page_contents/33/contained_images/d2a677cf6b68_127_Laptop paper image.jpg?1329317935" border="0" alt="" hspace="10" vspace="10" width="250" />Increasingly, paper-based documents add little value to  a  business but scanning and electronically tagging them could mean  those  that may have been difficult to access become relevant, secure and   quick to find.</p>\r\n<p>Our EDRMS system, <strong>m</strong>store, helps businesses to scan, organise, store and retrieve   documents electronically.  It easily integrates with bespoke and   industry-specific software including common packages for <a href="../../../page/edm-for-accounts-payable">accounting</a>, <a href="../../../page/edm-for-legal-and-professional-services"> legal case management,</a> HR, <a href="../../../page/edm-for-education">student records</a> etc.</p>\r\n<h2 class="no-top">Benefits:</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Improved customer service response - all your documents at your fingertips</li>\r\n<li>Improved efficiency - no more searching for paper documents</li>\r\n<li>Reduced workload surrounding audits and inspections</li>\r\n<li>Continuity planning - protection from fire, flood, theft or loss</li>\r\n<li>Document security - controlled access to sensitive data</li>\r\n<li>Reduced storage demands and costs</li>\r\n<li>Simplified and comprehensive regulatory compliance</li>\r\n<li>Remote access, 24/7 - from anywhere with an internet connection, including some mobile devices.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2>Download our free guides</h2>\r\n<p>A consultation with one of our experts can very quickly point you in the right direction when it comes to improving efficiencies within your organisation. In the meantime we have produced a number of helpful guides which you can use to help you answer some basic questions.</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><a href="../../../free-guides-31-ways-to-reduce-paper-usage.pdf">31 Ways to Reduce Paper Usage</a></li>\r\n<li><a href="../../../free-guides-top-tips-on-data-protection.pdf">Top Tips on Data Protection</a></li>\r\n<li><strong></strong><strong></strong><strong></strong><strong></strong><strong></strong><strong></strong><a href="../../../assets/stored_documents/original/108_ARENA_mstore_Overview.pdf" target="_blank"><strong>m</strong>store, software for electronic document management</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2>Useful Links</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><a href="../../../articles/161"><strong>m</strong>store v4 - out now!</a></li>\r\n<li><a href="../../../articles/110">Questioning the Cost of Purchasing</a></li>\r\n<li><a href="../../../case_studies?service=Electronic+Document+Management">Case studies - <strong>m</strong>store in practice</a></li>\r\n</ul>', '2010-11-26 11:47:01', '2014-08-22 11:51:19', '', '', 1, 3, 0, NULL, 1, 0),
(34, 'mstore for Legal and Professional Services', 'edm_for_the_legal_sector_and_professional_services', 'mstore for Legal and Professional Services', 39, 0, 0, 1, '2010-04-29 08:55:42', '<p class="introduction"><img class="image_right" src="../../../assets/page_contents/34/contained_images/b86ab518d67f_122_iStock_000015959628Medium.jpg?1329139417" border="0" alt="" hspace="0" width="180" /><span class="introduction">A medium-sized law firm is typically paying between &pound;50k and &pound;100k a year &ndash; or 7% of operating expenses - on annual storage costs. In other professions, such as financial services, increased regulation has resulted in greater document storage requirements, related costs and management time.</span></p>\r\n<p>Arena&rsquo;s <strong>m</strong>store software is compatible with industry specific software such as Linetime&rsquo;s case management software and Liberate. <strong>&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n<p><strong>m</strong>store is very flexible and highly configurable. Arena is the software author; affording you specialist knowledge, quick support response and configuration flexibility.</p>\r\n<h2>Benefits Arena&rsquo;s mstore brings to the legal sector:</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Links to your case management system for easy indexing and speedy retrieval of documents</li>\r\n<li>Creation of one single file per set of case documents for third party distribution</li>\r\n<li>Reduction in lost employee hours searching for files, often stored off-site</li>\r\n<li>Getting mail to fee earners quickly and securely - on-site or working remotely.</li>\r\n<li>Viewing and storing emails from programmes such as MS Outlook.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2>Downloads:</h2>\r\n<p>Details about the features and functionality of <strong>m</strong>store and our Hosted Services for remotely accessing your documents.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><a href="../../../assets/stored_documents/original/103_Arena EDM_Hosted_Services_v3.pdf" target="_blank">Hosted Services Brochure (PDF)</a></p>\r\n<p><a href="../../../assets/stored_documents/original/23_460 Brochure MSTORE 1 Page.pdf" target="_blank"><strong>m</strong>store brochure (PDF)</a></p>\r\n<h2>Further Information:</h2>\r\n<p><a href="../../../page/electronic-document-management">More about <strong>m</strong>store</a></p>', '2010-11-26 11:48:32', '2015-04-10 10:16:22', '', '', 1, 3, 0, NULL, 1, 0),
(35, 'mstore for Education', 'edm_for_education_', 'mstore for Education', 40, 0, 0, 1, '2010-04-29 08:55:42', '<p class="introduction"><img class="image_right" src="../../../assets/page_contents/35/contained_images/6a59e5d9d0b4_118_Tina McGuffie Grange School 2 .jpg?1329134277" border="0" alt="" hspace="0" width="180" />Arena works with many clients in the education sector,&nbsp;helping them with the common&nbsp;issues they face relating to the management, control and&nbsp;security of their vital documents.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>The Arena Group has developed&nbsp;<strong>m</strong>store for Education,&nbsp;its own electronic document and records management&nbsp;system (EDRMS). <strong>m</strong>store delivers a user-friendly mechanism to improve the whole document storage, retrieval and archiving process, whilst adding a level of security and functionality to improve&nbsp;legal compliance and the security of critical files.</p>\r\n<p>The software links with function or sector specific&nbsp;applications already in&nbsp;use within many education organisations (eg; SIMS). This means it is quick to install and implement, causing minimal disruption and delivering a host of benefits.</p>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;mstore for Education Benefits</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Legal Compliance: m</strong>store&nbsp;enables you to comply with<strong> </strong>legislation such as BS10008, the Freedom of Information Act 2000, Data Protection Act 1998 and Public Records Acts 1958/1967.</li>\r\n<li><strong>Safeguarding: m</strong>store automatically records who has viewed information and how often whilst also tracking document modifications without deleting original files.&nbsp; In addition, different users can be given different levels of access giving you a high level of security and protecting records from loss.</li>\r\n<li><strong>Accessibility:</strong> Any document can be attached to an <strong>m</strong>store record, including emails. Records are kept together in one central location, creating an efficient way to share documents, preventing loss and providing a greater level of control. </li>\r\n<li><strong>Document retention and archiving: &nbsp;m</strong>store records and flags up document expiry dates, ensuring all records are up to date for audits, including OFSTED inspections. Documents that have reached the end of their retention period can be flagged for deletion, reducing the time required to manually sort and archive paper records.&nbsp; </li>\r\n<li><strong>Decreased copy and print volumes:</strong> As a result of a reduction in the circulation of paper documents within the workplace, helping you to meet your sustainability goals and reducing related costs.</li>\r\n<li><strong>Disaster recovery:</strong> Documents are protected from loss through fire, theft and flood.</li>\r\n<li><strong>Efficiency: </strong>Working with electronic documents&nbsp;instead of paper reduces time associated with&nbsp;filing, retrieving, sharing, processing and archiving&nbsp;documents</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2>Downloads</h2>\r\n<p><a href="../../../assets/stored_documents/original/89_ARENA_mstoreEducation.pdf" target="_blank">EDRMS in Education (PDF)</a></p>\r\n<p><a href="../../../assets/stored_documents/original/63_Papers on Rec Mment Education 102013v1_WebsiteVersion.pdf" target="_blank">6 Paper Series: Records Management in Education (PDF)</a></p>\r\n<p><a href="../../../assets/stored_documents/original/90_ARENA_mstore_ARCHIVING_Education.pdf" target="_blank">Scanning Bureau for Education (PDF)</a></p>\r\n<h2>Further Information</h2>\r\n<p><a href="../../../articles/149?tag=Expert+News">VIDEO: Compliance in Education</a></p>\r\n<p><a href="../../../page/electronic-document-management">More about <strong>m</strong>store</a></p>', '2010-11-26 11:49:38', '2014-11-11 15:55:11', '', '', 1, 7, 0, NULL, 1, 0),
(36, 'IT', 'it', 'IT', 41, 0, 0, 1, '2010-04-29 08:55:42', '<p><img class="image_left" src="../../../assets/page_contents/36/contained_images/c2738c2e8688_42_ArenaIT.jpg?1297852995" border="0" alt="" hspace="0" width="100" /><span class="introduction">Arena has its own IT department and consultancy that can supply and install everything from a laptop to a fully networked system. We can provide general IT support, such as back-up to an in house IT department, or take over the entire IT function.</span></p>\r\n<p class="introduction">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Our IT specialists are already part of the team at many of the organisations we work with.&nbsp; For example, where printers are linked to a network or where our own software <strong>m</strong>store is used for electronic document management.</p>\r\n<p>As we have our own in-house experts we can often create a solution to a particular IT problem.&nbsp; &nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2>How we can help:</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Carrying out a free comprehensive IT survey followed-up with recommendations</li>\r\n<li>Supplying and servicing PCs and laptops</li>\r\n<li>Installing and maintaining your complete IT system</li>\r\n<li>Providing support to your existing IT department</li>\r\n</ul>', '2010-11-26 11:51:47', '2011-06-07 15:29:35', '', '', 1, 3, 0, NULL, 1, 0),
(37, 'Customer Feedback', 'feedback', 'Customer Feedback', 42, 0, 0, 1, '2010-04-29 08:55:42', '', '2010-11-26 12:32:28', '2011-01-13 15:29:30', '', '', 1, 1, 0, NULL, 1, 0);
