(56, 'Download our Brocure', 'download_our_brocure', 'Download our Brocure', 61, 0, 0, 1, '2010-04-29 08:55:42', NULL, '2011-02-16 17:41:48', '2011-02-16 17:43:28', NULL, NULL, 1, 1, 1, '2011-02-16 17:43:28', 1, 0),
(57, 'Arena in Education Brochure', 'arena_in_education_brochure', 'Arena in Education Brochure', 62, 0, 0, 1, '2010-04-29 08:55:42', '/Arena in Education Brochure_2012_Email_Version.pdf', '2011-02-17 10:53:54', '2012-12-21 09:33:57', NULL, NULL, 1, 1, 0, NULL, 1, 0),
(58, 'About Us', 'about_us', 'About Us', 18, 0, 0, 1, '2010-04-29 08:55:42', '<p><img src="../../../assets/page_contents/18/contained_images/ebe4d68483bd_4_about_us.jpg?1294327783" border="0" alt="" hspace="0" /></p>\r\n<p class="introduction">Arena Group specialises in hard copy and electronic document management. We provide the hardware, software, service and expertise that enables organisations to cut costs, improve efficiencies and become greener.</p>\r\n<p>We help your business to copy, print, scan, distribute, archive and retrieve documents.</p>\r\n<h2>An ethical supplier</h2>\r\n<p>We started out in 1991, when the photocopying market was at an all-time low &ndash; sales practices and service were so poor, our industry was even in the government spotlight.</p>\r\n<p>Six of us set up Arena because we thought there was a better way to do this &ndash; four of us have since retired but two are still in the business, which is privately owned.</p>\r\n<p>Initially we just sold and serviced photocopiers but over the years we have added a consultancy specialising in <a href="../../../page/electronic-document-management">electronic document management (EDM)</a>.  As technologies have developed and converged we now do pretty much everything you need to manage documents efficiently <a href="../../../page/products"></a><a href="../../../page/products-and-services"></a>and link them into your business systems.</p>\r\n<p>From the beginning our goal was to be ethical and honest, only selling what was best for the customer, giving them the best service of anyone in the industry &ndash; and keeping our customers for years.</p>\r\n<h2>An award winning employer and service provider</h2>\r\n<p>As we have grown from 10 employees in one small location to a company employing around 160 people across 6 UK offices, our original values and ethics still drive the way we do business. <strong>98% of our customers said they would recommend us and 99% rated the competency and helpfulness of our engineers</strong>. <br /> <br />We knew at the start that the way we treated and looked after our people would be critical to delivering this great service.  We need happy employees who deliver outstanding customer satisfaction &ndash; from the teams who pack up your toners to our frontline sales team and service engineers.</p>\r\n<p>We invest in retaining our talent and since 1994 have run our own <a href="../../../page/apprenticeship-programme">Apprentice Academy</a> that trains our service engineers.  We encourage and support employees to keep learning and developing their skills - whether studying for a professional qualification or an MBA.</p>\r\n<p>All this has been regularly recognised with top national and regional awards for our <a href="../../../surveys">outstanding customer service</a> and for being a good employer</p>\r\n<h3>Our Awards</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><span class="font_blue">Best company:</span> In 2008 we were listed by the Yorkshire Post as one of the region&rsquo;s best companies to work for and listed in 2006 by the Sunday Times as one of the best companies to work for.</li>\r\n<li><span class="font_blue">Service excellence:</span> The Chamber of Commerce has awarded Arena regional and national awards for outstanding customer service. </li>\r\n<li><span class="font_blue">Outstanding employer: </span>In addition to our recognition as one of the region''s best companies to work for, Arena hold Investors In People accreditation. Through looking after our people we maintain the best service for our customers and long-serving staff.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2>Dedicated to corporate social responsibility</h2>\r\n<p>Supporting our local community is really important to us.  All our employees are encouraged to make a contribution to their communities with many of our activities focused on helping children and young people.</p>\r\n<h2>Our Mission</h2>\r\n<p>By working as a focused team to deliver unbeatable levels of customer satisfaction we will become the UK''s best supplier of document solutions.</p>\r\n<h2>Our Values</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><span style="text-decoration: underline;"><strong>Service</strong></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>We are committed to delivering service excellence</strong></p>\r\n<p>We are dedicated to being the best at what we do; understanding our customers'' needs and doing everything it takes to deliver upon these needs</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><span style="text-decoration: underline;"><strong>Teamwork</strong></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>We are committed to working as one team towards a common goal</strong></p>\r\n<p>We are all in it together, supporting each other to deliver our collective targets and objectives</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><span style="text-decoration: underline;"><strong>Enjoyment</strong></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>We are committed to creating an atmosphere where people can enjoy their jobs</strong></p>\r\n<p>We recognise the need for fun, encourage humour and celebrate success</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><span style="text-decoration: underline;"><strong>People</strong></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>We are committed to our people</strong></p>\r\n<p>We will passionately recruit and develop talented individuals who enthusiastically go the extra mile for customers and colleagues alike</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><span style="text-decoration: underline;"><strong>Standards</strong></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>We are committed to the highest professional and ethical standards</strong></p>\r\n<p>Trust, honesty, integrity, respect and loyalty are qualities we constantly strive to exhibit&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n</ul>', '2010-11-23 13:04:01', '2015-04-08 07:56:11', '', '', 3, 3, 0, NULL, 1, 0),
(59, 'The Arena Story', 'the_arena_story', 'The Arena Story', 53, 0, 0, 0, '2010-04-29 08:55:42', '<p>Arena came into being in October 1991. At the start, the workforce comprised of six partners, three sales staff and a secretary. Of the original ten employees, six are still part of Arena Group and this low turnover of staff continues today. The Company started with no customers and the first Partners meeting was held in a mobile caravan. During those first few years everyone worked every hour possible and since then the company has grown to encompass 5 sites employing around 120 people.</p>\r\n<p><strong>1993</strong> - Arena achieved Major Account Status with Toshiba. The Systems Division was set up, as the Company worked to expand in a developing area. The use of and possibilities for copiers to be networked to computers became a reality and the Systems Division started selling, installing and servicing networks, computers, and printers.</p>\r\n<p><strong>1994</strong> - The Company achieved ISO9002 registration, which meant that we were achieving consistent high standards of quality on all the work we undertook. In the same year, the Company achieved the status of Investors In People from the Training and Enterprise Council.</p>\r\n<p><strong>1996</strong> - The Company moved its administrative facility to its present location at Armitage House.</p>\r\n<p><strong>1999</strong> - With the acquisition of COS UK Limited, the Company became the largest distributor of Toshiba Copiers and Facsimile Machines in the UK.</p>\r\n<p><strong>2001</strong> &ndash; Arena Group acquired CP Independent.</p>\r\n<p><strong>2003</strong> - Arena Group acquired Sterling Business Systems and WRG Limited.</p>\r\n<p><strong>2005</strong> - Office 21 became part of the Arena Group and then M&amp;S Reprographics Limited based in Bolton, Lancashire came under the Arena umbrella. This acquisition offered a superb opportunity for the group to develop and grow in the North West of England.</p>\r\n<p><strong>2006</strong> - Mitral Systems Ltd joined Arena Group - one of the leading providers of Workflow, Document Management and bespoke software solutions. From a beautiful rural base on the outskirts of Huddersfield this specialist team have a client base which covers the UK and beyond. The addition of Mitral into the Arena Group family creates the perfect platform for the Company to move away from selling and servicing just photocopiers to the development and implementation of a Company who provide document management solutions.&nbsp;Arena appeared in the Sunday Times 100 Best Small Companies to Work for list and won the National Chamber of Commerce award for Excellence in People Development.</p>\r\n<p><strong>2007</strong> - Launch of CSR community projects with Leeds Ahead and Barnardos. All Arena employees are encouraged to volunteer two days annually to help with charitable community projects. In 2007 Arena became a Patron of the Leeds, York and North Yorkshire Chamber of Commerce in support of regional businesses.</p>\r\n<p><strong>2008</strong> - Arena opened its dedicated service, training academy and logistics center in Garforth, Leeds. In 2008 we also won the British Chamber of Commerce award for Excellence in Customer Service.</p>\r\n<p><strong>2009</strong> - Arena entered a strategic partnership with Kyocera.</p>\r\n<p><strong>2010</strong> - Arena entered a strategic partnership with Konica Minolta, further expanding our copy and print portfolio.</p>', '2011-02-02 14:03:04', '2011-02-15 15:58:30', '', '', 4, 1, 0, NULL, 1, 0),
(60, 'Electronic Document Management (EDM)', 'electronic_document_management_edm', 'Electronic Document Management (EDM)', 38, 0, 0, 0, '2010-04-29 08:55:42', '<img class="image_left" src="../../..//assets/page_contents/33/contained_images/6beb3c4729db_43_ArenaEDM.jpg?1297853116" border="0" alt="" hspace="0" vspace="0" width="100" /><span class="introduction">Arena has a team of electronic document management (EDM) experts who can help you to streamline and improve your business processes.</span>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Our focus is always on your business &ndash; what can we do to make you more profitable, ensure security of documents, minimise your archive costs or speed up retrieval of documents?&nbsp; We work closely with you to understand your business and then produce workflow systems to develop with you.</p>\r\n<p>Our clients include education organisations, major corporates, public sector bodies, leisure businesses, professional services firms and banks.&nbsp; Names such as Leeds Building Society, DLA, Irwin Mitchell, BBC, P&amp;O Cruises, The Open University, MyTravel and the Department for Work and Pensions.</p>\r\n<p>We have created our own software, <strong>m</strong>store, which can be integrated into your business systems and with any existing software, whether bespoke or brand packages. <strong>m</strong>store is very flexible and highly configurable, because we are the software author, we can be flexible on customisation and development to meet your needs.</p>\r\n<h2>Just some of the business issues we can help you with include</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Scanning and indexing purchase orders, invoices and delivery notes</li>\r\n<li>Customer satisfaction surveys and analysis of issues</li>\r\n<li>Product tracking through a manufacturing process</li>\r\n<li>Rapid document archiving and retrieval for legal cases</li>\r\n<li>Email filing to ensure key information is not lost and can be quickly retrieved</li>\r\n<li>Reducing your carbon footprint and helping you to achieve your sustainability goals.</li>\r\n</ul>', '2010-11-26 11:47:01', '2011-02-16 10:45:46', '', '', 3, 1, 0, NULL, 1, 0),
(61, 'Our Service Statistics', 'our_service_statistics', 'Our Service Statistics', 63, 0, 0, 1, '2010-04-29 08:55:42', '<p class="introduction"><strong>97%</strong> of our clients score us at least 4 out of 5 for service and <strong>99%</strong> would recommend Arena*. We are dedicated to providing an outstanding level of service.</p>\r\n<table style="border: 0px; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td rowspan="4" valign="top">\r\n<p><img src="../../../assets/page_contents/61/contained_images/5403f416fba2_53_Engineer1.jpg?1302019199" border="0" alt="" hspace="0" width="250" /></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td valign="top"><span class="font_med">Average Response Time<br /></span></td>\r\n<td align="right" valign="top"><span class="font_med"><span class="font_blue"><strong>4hrs 45min</strong></span></span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td valign="top"><span class="font_med">First Time Fix </span></td>\r\n<td align="right" valign="top"><span class="font_med"><span class="font_blue"><strong>92.52%</strong></span></span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td valign="top"><span class="font_med">Uptime</span></td>\r\n<td align="right" valign="top"><span class="font_med"><span class="font_blue"><strong>99.04%</strong></span></span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td colspan="2" valign="top">\r\n<p>Uptime&nbsp;denotes the&nbsp;availability of all Arena print and copy devices during normal working hours (Monday-Friday, 9am-5pm).</p>\r\n<h6>Stats for the quarter April - June 2015.</h6>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<h2>Our Commitment to Training</h2>\r\n<p>In 2014 Arena''s service team undertook <strong><span class="font_blue">308 days </span></strong>of training.&nbsp;Our technicians&nbsp;commit to this high level of training&nbsp;to&nbsp;sustain their awareness and understanding of the devices they maintain.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2>First&nbsp;Time Fix Champions&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<p>We&nbsp;maintain a substantial stock of spare parts and consumables&nbsp; in our distribution centre and service team vehicles.</p>\r\n<p>This allows&nbsp;our&nbsp;engineers&nbsp;to carry substantial parts and consumables with them, enabling quick fixes and minimising machine down time.&nbsp;It also reduces our need to order parts from manufacturers or return to fix devices, which can take time.</p>\r\n<h6>*<em>Feedback from a random sample of recent surveys&nbsp;completed&nbsp;by our Customer Relationship Managers who continually visit our clients to ensure that their needs are met.</em></h6>', '2011-04-05 15:42:05', '2015-07-14 08:43:01', '', '', 3, 7, 0, NULL, 1, 0),
(62, 'mstore Cost Calculator', 'edm_cost_calculator', 'mstore Cost Calculator', 64, 0, 0, 1, '2010-04-29 08:55:42', '', '2012-03-19 10:10:59', '2013-10-25 15:56:12', '', '', 1, 3, 0, NULL, 1, 0);
INSERT INTO `page_contents` (`id`, `navigation_title`, `url_title`, `title`, `page_node_id`, `completed`, `published`, `active`, `last_updated_at`, `main_content`, `created_at`, `updated_at`, `meta_description`, `meta_tags`, `created_by`, `updated_by`, `recycled`, `recycled_at`, `display`, `position`) VALUES
(63, 'Framework Agreements', 'framework_agreements', 'Framework Agreements', 65, 0, 0, 1, '2010-04-29 08:55:42', '<p class="introduction">Arena Group is&nbsp;accredited on a number of sector specific framework agreements for peace of mind that our products and services are of the highest quality and represent good value for money.</p>\r\n<table>\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td valign="top">\r\n<p><img src="../../../assets/page_contents/63/contained_images/c76c6f617598_235_pfh - Nominated Suppiler.jpg?1378119904" border="0" alt="" hspace="0" vspace="0" width="100" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td valign="top">\r\n<h2 class="font_med">Procurement for Housing (PfH)</h2>\r\n<p class="font_med"><a href="http://www.procurementforhousing.co.uk" target="_blank">www.procurementforhousing.co.uk</a></p>\r\n<p>Arena is PfH&rsquo;s number 1 nominated supplier for the provision of Photocopiers, Printers, Multi-Functional Devices (MFDs) and Office Based Managed Print Services (MPS).</p>\r\n<p>Arena was put through a stringent tender process by CEL Group, and our no. 1 position  confirms that our products and services are of the highest standard and offer exceptional value.</p>\r\n<p>PfH was set up by the CIH, NHF and HouseMark in 2004. It is the largest national procurement organisation dedicated to the needs of the social housing sector.</p>\r\n<p>PfH harnesses the collective purchasing power of registered providers to reduce procurement costs and reinvest resources. The consortium has 850 Members, managing over 3.85 million properties.</p>\r\n<p>Members represent over 70% of the UK&rsquo;s social housing stock, spend almost &pound;3 million a week through PfH agreements and save over &pound;40 million a year. Membership is open to all UK housing associations, ALMOs and local authorities.</p>\r\n<p><a href="../../../assets/stored_documents/original/51_PfH Framework information.pdf" target="_blank">Further information - PfH documents (PDF)</a></p>\r\n<p><a href="http://www.procurementforhousing.co.uk/services/mini_competitions" target="_blank">PfH Guidance on Mini Competitions</a></p>\r\n<p><a href="../../../articles/93" target="_blank">Further information - News on our nomination</a></p>\r\n<p><a href="http://www.procurementforhousing.co.uk/what-we-do/procurement-services/" target="_blank">About PfH - Creating efficiencies&amp; driving performance</a></p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td valign="top">&nbsp;</td>\r\n<td valign="top">&nbsp;</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td valign="top"><img id="il_fi" style="padding-bottom: 8px; padding-right: 8px; padding-top: 8px;" src="http://www.renrayhealthcare.com/images/WEB_IHP_Logo.jpg" alt="" width="100" />&nbsp;</td>\r\n<td valign="top">\r\n<h2 class="font_med">Independent Healthcare Procurement (IHP)</h2>\r\n<p class="font_med"><span style="color: #000000;"><a href="http://www.ihponline.co.uk" target="_blank">www.ihponline.co.uk</a></span></p>\r\n<p>Having purchased for independent healthcare organisations since 1994, IHP have the expertise to source the best suppliers. Arena Group focus on delivering the best service as an approved supplier of Photocopiers, Printers, Multi-Functional Devices (MFDs) and Office Based Managed Print Services (MPS) on this framework.</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td valign="top">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</td>\r\n<td valign="top"><br /></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>', '2012-07-04 15:47:47', '2014-08-01 15:44:07', '', '', 3, 7, 0, NULL, 1, 0),
(64, 'Academies Show', 'academies_show', 'Academies Show', 66, 0, 0, 1, '2010-04-29 08:55:42', '', '2012-09-21 13:01:16', '2012-09-21 13:03:50', '', '', 3, 3, 1, '2012-09-21 13:03:50', 1, 0),
(65, 'Arena In Education Brochure EDM', 'arena_in_education_brochure_edm', 'Arena In Education Brochure EDM', 67, 0, 0, 0, '2010-04-29 08:55:42', '/Arena in Education Brochure_2012_Email_Version.pdf', '2012-12-21 09:46:42', '2012-12-21 09:49:02', '', '', 1, 1, 0, NULL, 1, 0),
(66, 'mstore for Credit Unions', 'arena_in_credit_unions', 'mstore for Credit Unions', 68, 0, 0, 1, '2010-04-29 08:55:42', '<p class="introduction"><img style="float: right;" src="../../../assets/page_contents/66/contained_images/31adde0fbd29_174_iStock_000020054949Medium.jpg?1357218084" border="0" alt="" hspace="0" vspace="0" width="180" />Credit Unions must balance legal requirements relating to the handling of confidential documents and data with the need to deliver excellent customer service in a competitive environment.</p>\r\n<p>Many credit unions are dealing with more customers than ever as a result of the tough economic climate. Increasing volumes of documentation that must be processed and managed, presenting a growing challenge, especially for those with limited resources.</p>\r\n<p>The Arena Group has developed&nbsp;<strong>m</strong>store for Credit Unions,&nbsp;its own electronic document and records management&nbsp;system (EDRMS). <strong>m</strong>store delivers a user-friendly mechanism to improve the whole document storage, retrieval and archiving process, whilst adding a level of security and functionality to improve&nbsp;legal compliance and the security of critical files.</p>\r\n<p>The software links with function or sector specific&nbsp;applications already in&nbsp;use within many UK credit unions. This means it is quick to install and implement, without disruption.</p>\r\n<h2>Benefits to the sector:</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Responsiveness: </strong>In an increasingly competitive industry, efficient processes and prompt responses to customer queries are essential.</li>\r\n<li><strong>Compliance:&nbsp;</strong><strong>m</strong>store enables you to comply with legal obligations relating to the security of your custoimer data, including BS10008, whilst also operating within FSA guidelines.</li>\r\n<li><strong>Productivity:</strong> Increasing client numbers result in greater workload and higher volumes of documentation to process, store and manage. Robust IT infrastructure and adequate resources are critical to successful growth.</li>\r\n<li><strong>Efficiency: </strong>Working with electronic documents&nbsp;instead  of paper reduces time assciated with&nbsp;filing, retrieving, sharing,  processing and archiving&nbsp;documents</li>\r\n<li><strong>Cost effectiveness:&nbsp; </strong><strong>m</strong>store delivers efficiency savings that are key to increased productivity, financial savings and great front line customer service.&nbsp; </li>\r\n<li><strong>Decreased copy and print volumes:</strong> As a result of a reduction in the circulation of paper documents within the workplace, helping you to meet your sustainability goals and reducing related costs.</li>\r\n<li><strong>Disaster recovery:</strong> Documents are protected from loss through fire, theft and flood.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2>Downloads:</h2>\r\n<p><a href="../../../assets/stored_documents/original/109_ARENA_mstoreCUNIONS.pdf" target="_blank">EDRMS in Credit Unions (PDF)</a></p>\r\n<h2>Further information:</h2>\r\n<p><a href="../../../articles/153">Insight feature: digital revolution in UK credit unions</a></p>\r\n<p><a href="../../../page/electronic-document-management">More about <strong>m</strong>store</a></p>', '2013-01-03 12:42:13', '2014-07-11 13:57:36', '', '', 3, 7, 0, NULL, 1, 0),
(67, 'Careers at Arena - why join us?', 'join_the_arena_team', 'Careers at Arena - why join us?', 69, 0, 0, 1, '2010-04-29 08:55:42', '<p>Our current business plan requires us to recruit a significant number of high quality individuals over the next three years.</p>\r\n<p>Our philosophy is that motivated employees contribute to customer retention by providing world class customer service. We therefore invest in great people, most of whom stay with us for many years.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><img style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="../../../assets/page_contents/67/contained_images/6600fce5b199_193_170D4638.jpg?1362069055" border="0" alt="" hspace="0" vspace="0" width="250" /></p>\r\n<table style="padding: 0px; text-align: center;" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" width="432" height="0">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style="padding: 0px; text-align: center;" valign="top"><img style="float: left;" src="../../../assets/page_contents/67/contained_images/d86f2d8f991b_190_Red nose day 2011 005.jpg?1361893392" border="0" alt="" hspace="0" vspace="0" width="285" height="188" /></td>\r\n<td style="padding: 0;" valign="top"><img style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="../../../assets/page_contents/67/contained_images/d82e3f2ffa32_192_13.jpg?1361981379" border="0" alt="" hspace="0" vspace="0" width="250" />\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p>We are recognised for our commitment to customers and employees and this is evidenced by a number of awards we have received:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Yorkshire''s Best Company To Work For</li>\r\n<li>Sunday Times 100 Best Small Companies To Work For</li>\r\n<li>National Award For Customer Service Excellence</li>\r\n<li>National Award For People Development</li>\r\n<li>Investors in People</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>We are proud to have been awarded the <a href="../../../articles/165">Investors in People Bronze Accreditation</a>. Having held the standard accreditation since 1997, this shows Arena''s dedication to developing employees.</p>\r\n<p>If you feel you have what it takes to complement our existing team, please contact us &ndash; we&rsquo;d love to hear from you.</p>', '2013-02-13 14:17:04', '2014-05-13 13:34:58', '', '', 5, 7, 1, '2013-02-13 14:17:35', 1, 0),
(68, 'Remote Desktop Support (ISL)', 'remote_desktop_support_isl', 'Remote Desktop Support (ISL)', 70, 0, 0, 0, '2010-04-29 08:55:42', 'http://www.arenagroupservice.net/isl.html', '2013-02-19 16:05:05', '2013-02-19 16:15:57', '', '', 1, 1, 0, NULL, 1, 0),
(69, 'MDS_OLD', 'mds_old', 'MDS_OLD', 71, 0, 0, 1, '2010-04-29 08:55:42', '<p class="introduction">Research has shown that print spend accounts for  1 - 3% of annual revenue*. Addressing your print and copy strategy in  isolation can deliver cost savings and a more efficient way of working.  We also know that organisations spend between 5 and 15% of  their annual    revenue on document lifecycle costs**. So, a broader approach that  considers the way you   work  with documents across the board will  deliver a much more significant financial cost    saving.&nbsp; &nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>With this in mind, our MDS addresses the way your  organisation works  with paper and digital documents with the aim of  promoting efficiency,  reducing waste and minimising costs.</p>\r\n<p>Solutions  range from relatively simple ideas that focus on just one  element of  your document workflow. For example, we may look at  digitising a paper  archive or your mailroom. We could address a  particular paper-driven  process such as purchase order processing; or  look at refining your  print and copy systems and practices.</p>\r\n<p>Alternatively, we may review  and improve the way you work with  documents across the board, enhancing  your technical infrastructure and  integrating new tools and practices to  drive efficiency, reduce costs  and minimise waste in all areas of  document management including  creation, processing, storage and  disposal.</p>\r\n<h2>Our Approach<img style="float: right;" src="../../../assets/page_contents/2/contained_images/67833d120ef5_123_approach.png?1329144483" border="0" alt="" hspace="10" width="80" /></h2>\r\n<p>We never make assumptions about the businesses we serve.&nbsp;Our first  step is always to&nbsp;understand&nbsp;how your organisation operates before  we&nbsp;propose strategies that help you to:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Reduce costs</li>\r\n<li>Drive efficiencies </li>\r\n<li>Improve productivity</li>\r\n<li>Enhance the quality of your customer service</li>\r\n<li>Increase sustainability - helping you to be ''greener''</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2>Document Experts</h2>\r\n<p>Arena brings you over 20 years of experience in the  successful  design,  project management and installation of systems that  range in  size and  complexity. In any situation, improvements are led by  your  current  business needs, budget and timescale.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3><em>*Source: Gartner / **Source: IDC</em></h3>', '2013-02-26 14:28:36', '2013-02-26 14:29:24', '', '', 1, 1, 0, NULL, 1, 0),
(70, 'EDM_OLD', 'edm_old', 'EDM_OLD', 72, 0, 0, 1, '2010-04-29 08:55:42', '<p class="introduction"><img class="image_right" src="../../../assets/page_contents/33/contained_images/f77daf90116f_127_Laptop paper image.jpg?1329317935" border="0" alt="" hspace="0" width="180" />Increasingly,  paper-based documents add little value to a business but scanning and  electronically tagging them could mean those that may have been  difficult to access become relevant, secure and quick to find.</p>\r\n<p><strong><img class="image_left" src="../../../assets/page_contents/33/contained_images/989d6987401e_61_mstore4-with-witespace.jpg?1303981902" border="0" alt="" hspace="0" width="100" />m</strong>store  is Arena&rsquo;s own software to help businesses scan, organise, store and  retrieve documents electronically.&nbsp; It easily integrates with bespoke  and industry-specific software including common packages for accounting,  legal case management, HR, student records etc.</p>\r\n<p><strong>m</strong>store is very flexible and highly configurable, it  will mould around your business rather than you having to adapt to its  methodologies.&nbsp; Because we are the software authors, we can be flexible  on customisation and development to meet your needs.</p>\r\n<h2><strong>See what our&nbsp;clients say: <a href="../../../case_studies?service=Electronic+Document+Management" target="_blank"><strong><strong>Case studies</strong></strong></a></strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong></h2>\r\n<h2>Benefits</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Improved efficiency &ndash; all your documents at your fingertips</li>\r\n<li>Reduced workload surrounding audits and inspections</li>\r\n<li>Disaster recovery protection &ndash; from fire, flood, theft or loss</li>\r\n<li>Document security &ndash; controlled access to sensitive data</li>\r\n<li>Reduced storage demands and costs</li>\r\n<li>More comprehensive regulatory compliance</li>\r\n<li>Remote access, 24/7 - from anywhere with an internet connection,&nbsp;including&nbsp;some mobile devices.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2>Further Information</h2>\r\n<p>Details about the features and functionality of <strong>m</strong>store and our Hosted Services for remotely accessing your documents.</p>\r\n<p>See what our&nbsp;clients say:<strong> <a href="../../../case_studies?service=Electronic+Document+Management" target="_blank"><strong><strong>Case studies</strong></strong></a></strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><a href="../../../assets/stored_documents/original/46_ARENA_mstore.pdf" target="_blank">Electronic document management: Benefits (PDF)</a></p>\r\n<p><a href="../../../assets/stored_documents/original/30_Arena EDM_Hosted_Services_v2.pdf" target="_blank">Hosted Services Brochure (PDF)</a></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>&nbsp;</strong></p>', '2013-02-26 14:30:35', '2013-02-26 14:30:43', '', '', 1, 1, 0, NULL, 1, 0),
(71, 'COPY_AND_PRINT_OLD', 'copy_and_print_old', 'COPY_AND_PRINT_OLD', 73, 0, 0, 1, '2010-04-29 08:55:42', '<p><img class="image_right" src="../../../assets/page_contents/30/contained_images/6f75afcc85c6_45_ArenaCAP.jpg?1297854716" border="0" alt="" hspace="0" width="100" /><span class="introduction">We know there is no &lsquo;one size fits all&rsquo; when it comes to your print and copy strategy.</span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Whether you need one efficient photocopier or a bespoke <a href="../../../page/print---the-hidden-costs">managed print service&nbsp;(MPS)</a>,&nbsp;we will work with you to&nbsp;design the best solution for your&nbsp;needs, taking into consideration;</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>any special print requirements (eg; a need to print folded and stapled booklets.)</li>\r\n<li>how much&nbsp;print and copy you need to produce</li>\r\n<li>necessary controls, reports&nbsp;and/or restrictions</li>\r\n<li>your environmental targets</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2 class="font_blue">Our&nbsp;<a href="../../../page/print---the-hidden-costs">managed print service</a>&nbsp;could reduce your print and copy costs by upto <a href="../../../page/print---the-hidden-costs"><strong class="font_blue">30%</strong></a></h2>\r\n<h2>Free print audit</h2>\r\n<p>Our experts conduct a free&nbsp;audit looking at your current&nbsp;print and  copy devices, volumes, costs and requirements.&nbsp;We&nbsp;then&nbsp;present a  proposal to deliver efficiencies and a better controlled strategy.</p>\r\n<h2>Our partners</h2>\r\n<p>Because we are an independent supplier we regularly review the market  to source the most suitable products for our clients. Read more about <a href="../../../page/partners">our partners</a>.</p>', '2013-02-26 14:31:28', '2013-02-26 14:33:20', '', '', 1, 1, 0, NULL, 1, 0),
(80, 'Print Control', 'print_control', 'Print Control', 84, 0, 0, 1, '2010-04-29 08:55:42', '<p class="introduction">In our business and  personal lives, it''s reassuring to have information printed in black and white. Whether it''s a good novel or a utility bill, print remains an essential part of day-to-day life.</p>\r\n<p>However, how often do you hit the &lsquo;print&rsquo; button only to realise that your paper size or margins are set wrong, you''ve printed in colour when you didn''t need to - or you''ve accidentally printed 20 pages when you only wanted page one? Not to mention all of those forgotten and unclaimed pages left on the printer.</p>\r\n<h2>The problem of uncontrolled printing raises various concerns;</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>The increasing cost of printing and paper places a heavy burden on budgets</li>\r\n<li>Colour  printing is on  the rise, and this pushes up the cost of consumables</li>\r\n<li>Wasteful printing has a negative environmental impact</li>\r\n<li>Sensitive  documents printed on devices far away from the originating  computer or  device and/or subsequently forgotten about, pose a serious  security  risk.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>Managing this behaviour will, undoubtedly create serious financial savings, whilst cutting the waste will reduce your carbon footprint and minimising forgotten pages addresses security concerns.</p>\r\n<h2>We have&nbsp;some clever ways  to help you to &lsquo;think before you print&rsquo;</h2>\r\n<p>Arena can propose a variety of measures to suit the way you work and address these issues. Whether you need help to develop a new print and copy policy, or you choose to implement measures and technology to curb wasteful behaviour, we can support you in changing for the better.</p>\r\n<h2>Insights</h2>\r\n<p><a href="../../../articles/112?tag=Expert+News" target="_blank">Putting the Brakes on Wasteful Printing</a>: Our Professional Services Manager, Ian Fox, explains how technology can  be used to reduce wasteful, insecure and unnecessary printing.</p>\r\n<h2>Downloads</h2>\r\n<p><a href="../../../assets/stored_documents/original/81_Print Control Benefits - Commercial.pdf" target="_blank">The benefits of print control</a>: Ten key benefits from using print control software for business.</p>\r\n<p><a href="../../../assets/stored_documents/original/82_Print Control Benefits - Education.pdf" target="_blank">Print control in Education</a>: Ten key benefits of print control when used in education.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n</ul>', '2013-09-02 15:58:44', '2014-03-18 15:22:20', '', '', 3, 7, 0, NULL, 1, 0),
(81, 'Sales Graduate Programme', 'sales_graduate_trainee_program', 'Graduate Account Manager – Leeds/Wakefield', 85, 0, 0, 1, '2010-04-29 08:55:42', '<p class="introduction"><img style="float: right;" src="../../../assets/page_contents/81/contained_images/677ca9946352_241_iStock_000013346702Medium.jpg?1381829746" border="0" alt="" hspace="0" vspace="0" width="250" /></p>\r\n<h1 class="introduction">Let me introduce Arena Group, we specialise in document management, providing the hardware, software, service and expertise that enables organisations to cut costs, improve efficiencies and become greener.</h1>\r\n<p><strong>And if you consider that businesses spend up to 3% every year on printing alone, document management really is big business!</strong><br /><br />But this isn&rsquo;t the reason that our Company is growing year on year - we think it has much more to do with the fact that 98% of our customers recommend us. And we know that to achieve these levels of service and success, that our people are vital.<br /><br /> Therefore we&rsquo;re looking for 4 confident, motivated graduates who are keen to take on responsibility quickly and accelerate their career. In return, we offer the chance to join a fast-growing and ambitious company, gaining the type of exposure and opportunity to make a difference that you can only get by working in an SME.</p>\r\n<h2><strong>The Scheme</strong></h2>\r\n<p>From day one, you&rsquo;ll be working in a rotation of the business, developing your skills and working within key areas of our business for a month at a time, such as Business Development, Consultancy and Customer Relationship Management.<br /><br /> Within 12 months, you will fly solo as a Graduate Account Manager with your own regional area. You&rsquo;ll be responsible for consulting and ultimately, selling a range of our solutions to customers in business and the public sector, managing and developing your own area.</p>\r\n<h2>So Why Join Arena?</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>A successful and growing company</li>\r\n<li>Full control of your own earnings potential</li>\r\n<li>Autonomy and responsibility at work</li>\r\n<li>You&rsquo;ll always be a person to us, never a      number, no matter how large we get</li>\r\n<li>We&rsquo;ll train you for a fantastic career,      whether this is on products or skill development, you&rsquo;ll always be at the      &lsquo;top of your game&rsquo;</li>\r\n<li>We offer excellent career prospects for those      who work hard</li>\r\n<li>Excellent incentives such as trips abroad and      in the UK to reward hard work</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2><strong>What We&rsquo;re Looking For</strong></h2>\r\n<p>Candidates looking to achieve (or already have) a 2:1 degree, but most importantly you&rsquo;ll be:<br /><br /></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Passionate about sales, with real &lsquo;star      quality&rsquo;.</li>\r\n<li>An excellent communicator with an ability to      engage with people.</li>\r\n<li>Forward-thinking, and motivated with a      positive attitude.</li>\r\n<li>Customer-focused.</li>\r\n<li>A keen networker who loves meeting new people.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2>If you are interested, we&rsquo;d love to hear from you. We are looking for 2 people to join us in Winter 2014 and 2 in Summer 2015.</h2>\r\n<h2>Send your CV &amp; Cover Letter to <a href="mailto:graduates@arenagroup.net">graduates@arenagroup.net.</a></h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n</ul>', '2013-10-10 08:33:29', '2014-10-06 08:34:32', '', '', 7, 7, 0, NULL, 1, 0),
(82, 'mstore for Motor Dealerships', 'mstore_for_motor_dealerships', 'mstore for Motor Dealerships', 86, 0, 0, 1, '2010-04-29 08:55:42', '<p class="introduction"><img class="image_right" src="../../../assets/page_contents/82/contained_images/3803a863c0b0_255_iStock_000011181273Medium.jpg?1386255079" border="0" alt="" hspace="0" width="180" />Speed, accuracy and cost are vital to the smooth operation of UK motor dealerships. Integration of supply chain systems and processes alongside fast and accurate communication between multiple stakeholders is key to closing and delivering sales in a timely manner.</p>\r\n<p>The management and storage of documents often represents a cost and efficiency burden for UK motor dealerships, for several reasons;</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Stringent legislation surrounding document / data processing, retention, compliance audit and security.</li>\r\n<li>Scarce and costly storage space for paperwork such as deal files.</li>\r\n<li>Dispersed data / documents cannot be shared by multiple people simultaneously, or quickly accessed.</li>\r\n<li>Difficulties in finding documents when responding to enquiries or audits.</li>\r\n<li>Potential crises such as fires and floods present data recovery risks.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>The Arena Group has developed&nbsp;<strong>m</strong>store for Motor Dealerships,&nbsp;its own electronic document and records management&nbsp;system (EDRMS). Working alongside your existing dealer management system, <strong>m</strong>store allows you to store, share, reference, move, track and process documents quickly and efficiently in electronic format. This has multiple benefits which all result in cost savings for your business.</p>\r\n<h2>Deal files</h2>\r\n<p>Motor dealerships will enjoy the variety of benefits that <strong>m</strong>store&nbsp; delivers to any business including compliance, collaboration and efficiency. However, for those working with paper-based deal files, there is even more value to be gained.</p>\r\n<p>Paper-based deal files present a particular problem due to their size, complexity and the number of stakeholders required to contribute to them. By its very nature a paper-based deal file can only ever be in one place at one time, presenting difficulties in terms of access for everyone who requires it. Arena&rsquo;s <strong>m</strong>store addresses these problems;</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Once scanned into <strong>m</strong>store, original paperwork can be disposed of to address any storage issues.</li>\r\n<li>Documents and data in <strong>m</strong>store can be accessed by multiple people at the same time for a fast and efficient sale process.</li>\r\n<li>Managers can track a deal''s progress, monitor compliance to company  procedures and ensure the required events and documents are coming  together in the right sequence and at the right time.</li>\r\n<li>Individuals required to take action can be  automatically prompted.</li>\r\n<li><strong>m</strong>store integrates with major Dealer Management Systems to populate the <strong>m</strong>store deal file with stock codes, chassis and registration numbers etc.</li>\r\n<li>Access to the digital deal file is available within seconds for an immediate customer service response.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2>Downloads:</h2>\r\n<p><a href="../../../assets/stored_documents/original/88_ARENA_mstoreMOTOR_DEALERS.pdf" target="_blank">EDRMS in UK Motor Dealerships (PDF)</a></p>\r\n<h2>Further Information:</h2>\r\n<p><a href="../../../page/electronic-document-management">More about <strong>m</strong>store</a></p>', '2013-12-05 14:48:28', '2014-04-15 09:16:40', '', '', 3, 7, 0, NULL, 1, 0),
(85, 'Thank You', 'thank_you', 'Thank You', 89, 0, 0, 1, '2010-04-29 08:55:42', '<p>Your details have been added to our mailing list. Many thanks for subscribing to our emails.</p>\r\n<p>The Arena Team.</p>', '2013-12-10 17:23:59', '2013-12-10 17:24:04', '', '', 3, 3, 0, NULL, 1, 0),
(86, 'Our Awards and Accreditations', 'our_awards_and_accreditations', 'Our Awards and Accreditations', 90, 0, 0, 1, '2010-04-29 08:55:42', '<h2>An award winning employer and service provider</h2>\r\n<p>Arena has been regularly recognised with top national and regional awards for our <a href="../../../surveys">outstanding customer service</a> and for being a good employer.</p>\r\n<h3>Our Awards</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><span class="font_blue">Best company:</span> In 2008 we were listed  by the Yorkshire Post as one of the region&rsquo;s best companies to work for  and listed in 2006 by the Sunday Times as one of the best companies to  work for.</li>\r\n<li><span class="font_blue">Service excellence:</span> The Chamber of Commerce has awarded Arena regional and national awards for outstanding customer service. </li>\r\n<li><span class="font_blue">Outstanding employer: </span>In addition to  our recognition as one of the region''s best companies to work for, Arena  hold Investors In People accreditation. Through looking after our  people we maintain the best service for our customers and long-serving  staff.</li>\r\n<li><a href="../../../articles/195">Employer of the Year:</a> We invest in retaining our talent and since 1994 have run our own <a href="../../../page/apprenticeship-programme">Apprentice Academy</a>.  We encourage and support employees   to keep learning and developing their skills - whether studying for a   professional qualification or an MBA. In 2013 and 2014 Arena was awarded Employer of The Year at the Leeds Apprenticeship Awards for our outstanding commitment to apprenticeships. </li>\r\n</ul>', '2014-04-24 07:49:12', '2014-04-24 07:58:04', '', '', 3, 3, 0, NULL, 1, 0),
(87, 'Arena in Housing Brochure', 'arena_in_housing_brochure', 'Arena in Housing Brochure', 91, 0, 0, 1, '2010-04-29 08:55:42', '/ArenaHousing.pdf', '2014-06-25 16:06:02', '2014-06-25 16:08:57', NULL, NULL, 1, 1, 0, NULL, 1, 0),
(88, 'Employee DBS Information', 'employee_dbs_details', 'Employee DBS Information', 92, 0, 0, 1, '2010-04-29 08:55:42', '<p>The Arena Group takes customer safety very seriously.&nbsp; Many of our customers have machinery or equipment based at educational establishments and consequently our customer facing staff often come into contact with children or vulnerable adults.</p>\r\n<p>As part of our commitment to provide our customers with support staff who are highly competent and appropriate for the environment, all customer facing staff undergo a DBS (formerly CRB) check.</p>\r\n<p>We appreciate that it is important for our customers to keep records of the DBS reference numbers and date of checks. Therefore to make it easier for you to access the information that you need quickly, the reference details can be found in the spreadsheet below.</p>\r\n<p><a href="../../../assets/stored_documents/original/124_DBS Website List (27.5.15).xlsx" target="_blank"></a><a href="../../../assets/stored_documents/original/126_Copy of DBS Website List (14 8 15).xlsx" target="_blank"><a href="../../../assets/stored_documents/original/127_DBS Website List (04 09 15).xlsx" target="_blank">Arena DBS Numbers</a></a><a href="../../../assets/stored_documents/original/124_DBS Website List (27.5.15).xlsx" target="_blank"></a></p>\r\n<p>Please note that the spread sheet is password protected. For customers wishing to gain access for the first time, please call Laura Hood (HR Advisor), who can provide the password for the spreadsheet. This password should not be divulged to any other party.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Telephone:</strong> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 08448638000</p>\r\n<p><strong>Email:&nbsp;&nbsp;</strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <a href="mailto:laurah@arenagroup.net">laurah@arenagroup.net</a></p>', '2015-04-08 11:28:37', '2015-09-04 10:27:16', '', '', 7, 7, 0, NULL, 1, 0);
