INSERT INTO `staff_testimonials` (`id`, `quote`, `author`, `created_by`, `updated_by`, `recycled`, `recycled_at`, `display`, `position`, `created_at`, `updated_at`) VALUES
(1, 'I''ve been at Arena since 2008, initially as an office assistant and now as an administrator. It’s probably already been said but people development is a an obvious benefit of working for Arena Group. Training is always available and always funded by the company.', 'Leah Whitelock, Administrator', 1, NULL, 0, NULL, 1, 0, '2011-02-07 16:06:02', '2011-02-07 16:06:02'),
(3, 'I''m fleet controller and accounts assistant and have been working with Arena since 2009. The managers at Arena are 100% committed to growing the company and its employees to ensure a better future for us all. This is especially so in these difficult financial times.', 'Danielle Hooks, Fleet Controller and Accounts Assistant', 1, 3, 0, NULL, 0, 0, '2011-02-07 16:10:32', '2013-08-01 12:23:02'),
(4, 'I ran the London Marathon and raised over £860 for the Wakefield Hospice with the help of my colleagues. Arena has a policy that it will match money pledged by staff for such charitable events and this raised my funds above £1700. This generosity is another reason why Arena Group is such an amazing company to work for.', 'Peter Maskill, Workshop Manager', 1, NULL, 0, NULL, 1, 0, '2011-02-07 16:10:54', '2011-02-07 16:10:54'),
(6, 'I''ve been working at Arena since 2005 as a sales executive. I’ve found that Arena don’t just look at the training and development of its employees inside work but management here is also understanding and supportive when employees meet with tough times outside of work. Arena will always endeavour to provide the necessary support to allow everyone to contribute towards the business, even in difficult times. This holistic approach towards recognising everyone as an individual with individual needs is something I value highly.', 'John Clark, Sales Executive', 1, NULL, 0, NULL, 1, 0, '2011-02-07 16:11:36', '2011-02-07 16:11:36'),
(7, 'I currently work in the Professional Services Team having started as an administrator at Arena. For me the constant incentives and awards that are used to motivate staff are what make Arena such a great place to work. In our department we have the Admin High Flyer Award and on a company wide scale such rewards as the Premier Conference help to maintain great standards of work.', 'Ryan Calton, Print Analyst', 1, NULL, 0, NULL, 1, 0, '2011-02-07 16:11:50', '2011-02-07 16:11:50'),
(8, 'There''s a good atmosphere at Arena. Everyone goes out of their way to look after their colleagues and help out whenever possible.', 'Ian Fox, Head of Professional Services', 1, NULL, 0, NULL, 1, 0, '2011-02-07 16:12:09', '2011-02-07 16:12:09'),
(9, 'I''m a sales account manager and have been working with Arena since 2003. Working at Arena is just as it should be with any other company: mutually beneficial. I get satisfaction from helping Arena to reach its goals but in turn I feel valued as an employee, not just a small cog in a very large wheel. In a nutshell, if you care about Arena the company cares about you.', 'Tim Bye, Account Manager', 1, NULL, 0, NULL, 1, 0, '2011-02-07 16:14:21', '2011-02-07 16:14:21'),
(10, 'I began working with Arena in 2002 as an accounts assistant and I’m now financial controller. Staff motivation and dedication has rewarded the business with maintaining steady profits over the last few years which has allowed us to guarantee against redundancies at the height of the recession.', 'Lisa Payne, Financial Controller', 1, NULL, 0, NULL, 1, 0, '2011-02-07 16:24:25', '2011-02-07 16:24:25'),
(11, 'I work in the call control team at Arena. I left my job and, although there was nothing wrong with my new job, I returned to Arena after four months because I missed my job and my colleagues. I’m really pleased to be back.', 'Jessica Jones, Call Coordinator', 1, 3, 0, NULL, 1, 0, '2011-02-07 16:24:38', '2013-08-01 12:23:22'),
(12, 'I’ve been employed by Arena Group since it started in 1991. Infectious enthusiasm makes Arena a great company to work for, everybody is listened to and motivated to work together for our mutual success. I’ve had many jobs in my life but I’ve stayed with Arena for so long because it’s a really great company to work for.', 'John Wall, Account Manager', 1, NULL, 0, NULL, 1, 0, '2011-02-07 16:53:03', '2011-02-07 16:53:03'),
(13, 'One of Arena''s mottos is "Work Hard, Play Hard" and that is certainly true. I like to do both of these things and employees at Arena are awarded in many different ways. Recently myself and my husband had the pleasure of being treated to a 5 star all inclusive weekend in Majorca, which was a great incentive for coming to work and performing in your job. This is on top of the annual conference which includes a meal and a night away somewhere in the UK, departmental days and nights out and various other social and charity events throughout the year which Arena funds.', 'Mishelle Williams, Sales Administrator', 1, 7, 0, NULL, 0, 0, '2011-02-08 12:59:46', '2014-04-16 11:24:51');
