(86, 'I was very impressed with the knowledge of your technical guys. They had the right approach, spoke my language and understood exactly what I was wanting even though I couldn’t explain it in technical terms.', 'Jill Pounder, Business Manager', 'Sherburn High School', '2015-08-25 12:41:42', '2015-08-25 12:41:42', 7, NULL, 0, NULL, 1, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', 30),
